---
const activities = [
  "Fund research",
  "Share knowledge",
  "Build tools",
  "Grow awareness about quantum biology",
];
---

<section class="bg-plum-dark text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8 max-w-3xl">
      What is the Quantum Biology DAO community?
    </h2>
    <div
      class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 font-sans text-base text-cream/80 leading-relaxed"
    >
      <p>
        The Quantum Biology community is a decentralized group of people
        (ranging from enthusiasts to quantum physicists) working at the
        intersection of quantum physics and biology.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're organized as a DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organization), which
        means our work is driven by the community, not by a single leader or
        company. Members come together to:
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 my-8">
      {
        activities.map((label) => (
          <span class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full border border-cream/30 text-cream text-sm font-sans">
            {label}
          </span>
        ))
      }
    </div>
    <p
      class="max-w-3xl font-sans text-base text-cream/80 leading-relaxed"
    >
      Through open collaboration and blockchain-based governance, we're creating
      a space where anyone can contribute to the future of science. <a
        href="/qbio-token"
        class="text-pink hover:text-pink-light underline underline-offset-2"
      >Learn more about the governance process here</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
